name: 💦WATER PROTECTION 👅💦
description:
The guards guard you from stalkers but you dropped the water. Without it you will not be able to continue the mission and the next source is miles away. 
A story that doesn't seem so bad, fortunately it's fiction but without water you won't survive. 
Let's take care of the water and as long as we have it nearby, let's drink it.
